items.title: Affinity Federal Credit Union President’s Invitational Golf Outing Raises $214,000 in Support of Affinity Foundation
items.description: BASKING RIDGE, N.J., July 21, 2025--Affinity Federal Credit Union ("Affinity") recently hosted its annual President’s Invitational Golf Outing, raising over $214,000 for the Affinity Foundation ("Foundation"). The event, held on June 9, 2025, welcomed 126 golfers along with additional guests and 35 sponsors.
